      "content": {
        "title": "Paediatric Spine Deformity — Scoliosis — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Idiopathic and congenital spinal curvature in children and adolescents requiring bracing or surgical correction.",
        "summary": "Lenke classification guides adolescent idiopathic scoliosis surgery. Early-onset scoliosis may use growing rods. Congenital scoliosis from vertebral anomalies."
      },
